== List of OpenRC users ==

An incomplete list of distributions and operating systems using OpenRC.

=== Default ===

On these systems OpenRC is the default init system.

* [https://alpinelinux.org/ Alpine Linux]
* [http://www.archbang.org/ ArchBang]
* Calculate Linux
* [http://www.funtoo.org/ Funtoo Linux]
* [https://www.gentoo.org/ Gentoo Linux]
** [[Gentoo FreeBSD]]
** [[Gentoo NetBSD]]
** [[Gentoo OpenBSD]]
* [https://www.system-rescue-cd.org/ SystemRescueCd]
* [https://www.trueos.org/ TrueOS] (FreeBSD based)

=== Optional ===

The following systems don't use OpenRC by default, but have users and packages to support OpenRC.

* [https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/OpenRC Arch Linux]
* [https://wiki.debian.org/OpenRC Debian]
* [https://git.devuan.org/devuan-packages/openrc Devuan]
* [https://sourceforge.net/projects/manjaro-openrc/ Manjaro]
* [https://wiki.parabola.nu/OpenRC Parabola]

